{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/socketclientprotocol\/onnotifylocaladdress(flags:handler:)"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyLocalAddress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"SocketClientRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketClientRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO15SocketClientRefV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"code":"notifyLocalAddress","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" signal is emitted","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"syntax":"C"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This represents the underlying ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::local-address"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"onNotifyLocalAddress(flags:handler:)","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO20SocketClientProtocolPAAE20onNotifyLocalAddress5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bC3RefV_AG09ParamSpecO0VtctF","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyLocalAddress"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"text":"SocketClientRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO15SocketClientRefV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"}],"extendedModule":"GIO","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketClientProtocol"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketClientProtocol\/onNotifyLocalAddress(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is